text:
West Farms Road (foreground), west side, north from Southern Boulevard (left), to but not including Hoe Ave. Across the 1-story building, on Southern Boulevard, appears the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Lexington Ave. subway line. Also shown is a general view northwestward as seen from the 8-story building at the S.W. corner of Hoe Avenue and East 165th Street.

May 1926.

Brown Brothers.
title: Bronx: West Farms Road - Southern Boulevard - Hoe Ave.
